data.description: This spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is perfect for a family.  It is an entertainers dream with the 3 living spaces, brick fire place and wood beams.  The large kitchen opening to the living room is perfect for keeping the conversation flowing while cooking up some delicious meals.  The guest bedrooms feature window seats and built ins.  There is a covered patio with a hot tub in the backyard is a great way to unwind.
